snippet.title: Leak Project
snippet.description:
The Leak Project was created to offer awareness, information and entertainment not found in the main stream media.  
Leak Project offers a refreshing approach to various topics and gives your mind a workout. We cover almost everything worth being covered here.
Live Shows, Check back daily for new content as we thrive to bring you the cutting edge in news, current events, on scene video footage, interviews and information.
Be the change you want to see
http://www.leakproject.com
